Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project

Class ProjectTableDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project.ProjectTableDto
public class ProjectTableDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for displaying project information in a table format. This class encapsulates the essential details of a project necessary for listing in a tabular view, including project photo, name, lab location, status, start and end dates, member count, and completion percentage.

    • ProjectTableDto

      public ProjectTableDto(String photo, String name, WorkLocalENUM lab, StateProjectENUM status, int numberOfMembers, Date startDate, Date finalDate, int maxMembers, boolean isMember, int percentageDone)
      Constructs a new ProjectTableDto with specified details.
      Parameters:
      photo - URL or path to the project's photo.
      name - Name of the project.
      lab - Lab location associated with the project.
      status - Current status of the project.
      numberOfMembers - Current number of members in the project.
      startDate - Start date of the project.
      finalDate - End date (expected or actual) of the project.
      maxMembers - Maximum allowed number of members in the project.
      isMember - Flag indicating if the current user is a member of the project.
      percentageDone - Percentage of the project completed.
